dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Rutherford and East Rutherford, Bergen Co., New Jersey (Sheet 9)
dct_description_sm: "June 1909." Includes key, streets and specials index, and text. "1595." Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-14, 20 and 28, showing Rutherford; sheets 15-19 and 21-27, showing East Rutherford, foldered separately.
